- module_ctrl8: Control Module 8 (Components that are part of the module: ctrl8_switch, ctrl8_green_led, ctrl8_green_resistor, ctrl8_cable_in_pos, ctrl8_cable_in_neg, ctrl8_cable_out_pos, ctrl8_cable_out_neg)
- module_load: Load Module (Components that are part of the module: main_bulb, internal_bulb, load_peephole, load_diode, load_cable_pos, load_cable_neg)

