- load_cable_neg: Load Input Cable (−)

Instruction: Visually inspect all control module LEDs (switch indicators), their holders, and wiring for mis-seating, installation direction issues, or physical damage. Check if the LEDs are properly installed and if any visible faults exist in the wiring, resistor, or switch areas.
